How to download the packages from web by using wget command
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
# wget <url-name>

============================
YUM(Yellowdog Updater Modified)
=============================

YUM is a package manager built on RPM that automatically resolve dependencies.

Advantages:
===========
Dependency management
Download packages automatically
Uses yum repositories 
Easy updates
 
Yum repository:  Repository is a storage location where Linux packages are kept.

# check repositories
$ yum repolist

# install packages
$ yum install wget -y  [ -y is nothing but automcatically answer "yes"]

# Update package
$ yum update wget

# remove package
$ yum remove wget

# update all packages
$ yum update

# search package
$ yum search wget

#get package information
$yum info wget

# list Installed packages
$ yum list installed

# check package history
$ yum history

# clean cache
$ yum clean all


